Package gw.api.system

Class TimeParameterKey

java.lang.Object
gw.api.system.ParameterKey<Date>
gw.api.system.TimeParameterKey
public class TimeParameterKey extends ParameterKey<Date>
Description/specification of a Time configuration parameter.

Values are standard XML format ("hh:mm:ss") times.
